---
title: GitHub API Sync Sequence
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI
    participant Lock as SyncLock
    participant Orch as SyncOrchestrator
    participant Cache as SyncCache
    participant GitHub as GitHub API
    participant Storage as repositories.yml
    
    User->>CLI: cargo run -- sync
    CLI->>Orch: Initialize(config)
    Orch->>Lock: try_lock(canonical_path)
    
    alt Lock acquired
        Lock-->>Orch: Exclusive lock held
    else Lock held by another process
        Lock-->>Orch: Error: "Another sync in progress"
        Orch-->>CLI: Return error
        CLI-->>User: ❌ Sync already running
    end
    
    Orch->>Cache: Load cache entries
    Cache-->>Orch: Existing cached data
    
    Orch->>Storage: Load repositories.yml
    Storage-->>Orch: Current repository list (800+ repos)
    
    Orch->>Orch: Start progress bar
    
    loop For each repository
        Orch->>Cache: Check if fresh (TTL < 24h)
        
        alt Cache HIT (fresh data)
            Cache-->>Orch: Use cached, skip API call
            Orch->>Orch: Increment cached counter
        else Cache MISS or stale
            Orch->>GitHub: GET /repos/:owner/:name<br/>(with auth token)
            
            alt 200 OK Success
                GitHub-->>Orch: Repository metadata<br/>(stars, description, license, etc.)
                Orch->>Orch: merge_sync_data()<br/>(preserve manual fields)
                Orch->>Cache: Update cache entry<br/>(timestamp, ETag, stars)
                Orch->>Orch: Increment synced counter
            else 404 Not Found
                GitHub-->>Orch: Repository not found
                Orch->>Orch: Mark as deprecated<br/>Continue with others
                Orch->>Orch: Increment failed counter
            else 403 Rate Limit
                GitHub-->>Orch: Rate limit exceeded
                Orch->>Orch: Wait for reset<br/>Then retry
            end
            
            Note over Orch,GitHub: Rate limit check<br/>every 100 repos
        end
        
        Orch->>Orch: Update progress bar
    end
    
    Orch->>Storage: Save updated repositories.yml<br/>(atomic write)
    Orch->>Cache: Persist cache to disk
    Orch->>Orch: Calculate sync statistics
    Note over Orch,Lock: SyncLock released on drop
    Orch->>CLI: Return SyncResult<br/>(synced, cached, failed, duration)
    CLI->>User: Display summary:<br/>✅ X synced, ⚠️ Y cached, ❌ Z failed

